(4, 'Call for Paper for ICECE 2020', '2020-08-20', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"buet.jpg\" style=\"width: 902px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dear Sir/Madam,</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We cordially invite you to submit papers in ICECE 2020, the 11th International Conference on Electrical and Computer Engineering, which is the pioneering international conference in the areas of electrical and computer engineering&nbsp; organized by the Department of Electrical and Electronic Engineering, Bangladesh University of Engineering and technology. ICECE 2020 will be held from <span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT81_com_zimbra_date\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 149); cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT102_com_zimbra_date\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\">December 17</span></span>-19, 2020 in a fully virtual mode.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ICECE brings together individuals from academia, research organizations, government, and industry, to discuss and share ideas and present their latest findings and experiences in the areas of electrical and computer engineering. All accepted and presented papers will be submitted to IEEE Xplore.® digital library.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For details, please visit:&nbsp; </span><span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT82_com_zimbra_url\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 149); cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT103_com_zimbra_url\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\"><a href=\"https://icece.buet.ac.bd/2020/index.php\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 149); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">https://icece.buet.ac.bd/2020/index.php</span></a></span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For call for paper, please visit :</span><span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT83_com_zimbra_url\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 149); cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT104_com_zimbra_url\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\"><a href=\"https://icece.buet.ac.bd/2020/call-for-papers.php\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 149); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">https://icece.buet.ac.bd/2020/call-for-papers.php</span></a></span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For important dates, please visit: </span><span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT84_com_zimbra_url\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 149); cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"Object\" role=\"link\" id=\"OBJ_PREFIX_DWT105_com_zimbra_url\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\"><a href=\"https://icece.buet.ac.bd/2020/important-dates.php\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 149); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">https://icece.buet.ac.bd/2020/important-dates.php</span></a></span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Please encourage your peers, friends, researchers, seniors, and students in your network to submit their quality submissions to ICECE 2020. We look forward to receiving your research contributions.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(80, 0, 80); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(80, 0, 80); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sincerely,</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; color: rgb(35, 31, 32); background-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ICECE 2020 Committee</span></p>', '2020-08-20 02:36:23', '2020-08-20 09:25:24');
