(66, 'Dr. S. Shahnawaz Ahmed', 'dr-s-shahnawaz-ahmed', 2, 'ssahmed@eee.buet.ac.bd', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">PhD, University of Manchester Institute\r\nof Science and Technology (UMIST), 1987</span><u1:p></u1:p><u2:p></u2:p><o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">MSc, BUET, 1984</span><u3:p></u3:p></span><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</span><u2:p></u2:p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">BSC, BUET, 1982</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '+88 01552 321 941', '20200212_1581481489.jpg', 1, '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1.“Laureate of the annual (2002)\r\ncompetition” by the Royal academy of Overseas Sciences, Belgium for the study\r\n“Photovoltaic Supplement to Diesel Generator Based Supply in an Off-grid\r\nLocation of East Malaysia” that was adjudged as the best one among the studies received\r\nunder the category of Technical Sciences from international researchers.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><u1:p></u1:p><u2:p></u2:p><o:p></o:p></p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2.“BAS-M.O. Ghani Gold Medal 2003” by Bangladesh\r\nAcademy of Sciences in recognition of contributions in the field of electrical\r\nand electronic engineering.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1. S. Shahnawaz Ahmed and Md.\r\nMohsin:&nbsp; “Analytical Determination of the Control Parameters for a Large\r\nPhotovoltaic Generator Embedded in a Grid System”, IEEE (USA) Transactions on\r\nSustainable Energy, Vol.2, No.2, April 2011, pp.122-130.</span><u1:p></u1:p></span><u2:p></u2:p><u3:p></u3:p><u4:p></u4:p><o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2. S. Shahnawaz Ahmed, Shah Muhammed Abid Hussain and Md.\r\nSayeed Salam:&nbsp; “A Novel Substitute for the Meter Readers in a Resource\r\nConstrained Electricity Utility”, IEEE (USA) Transactions on Smart Grid, Vol.4,\r\nNo.3, September 2013, pp.1615-1616.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">S.\r\nShahnawaz Ahmed, Mohammad Zunaidur Rashid, Kamruzzaman Khan and A.N.M. Wasekul\r\nAzad, “A Device for Multi-Criteria Load Management in a Power System”,\r\nBangladesh Patent No.1005480, Filing date: 01 August 2012</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">Modeling, simulation and real-time control of large-scale\r\npower and energy systems; Digital protection; Demand side management; Energy\r\nefficiency and conservation; Grid integration of renewables; Smart Grid; FACTS\r\ndevices; Electricity market; Regional or transnational power grid.</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">S. Shahnawaz Ahmed (Senior Member, IEEE)\r\nearned his B.Sc.Eng.(1982, BUET), M.Sc. Eng. (1984, BUET) and PhD (1987, UMIST,\r\nUK). He joined the EEE Dept., BUET in 1983 and has been serving as a full\r\nProfessor since 1996. He also served as a Professor in the Faculty of Electrical\r\nEngineering in Universiti Teknlogi Malaysia (UTM) in the years 2000-2003 on\r\nleave from BUET. He served as the Head, EEE Dept., Dean, EEE Faculty, Director,\r\nCentre for Energy Studies, and Director, P&amp;D in BUET, Director in PGCB and\r\nDPDC Boards, and Chairman of EEDC, BSTI. Currently he is a Director in DESCO\r\nBoard. He teaches, supervises research and provides consultancy services in\r\nplanning, real time operation and control of power system including smart grid,\r\nelectricity market, nuclear power and renewable energy. He has authored or\r\ncoauthored more than 60 publications in peer reviewed journals and conferences.\r\nHe has supervised 12 Masters’ theses and 3 PhD theses. Further information on\r\nhim can be obtained from the URL http://ssahmed.buet.ac.bd/.</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'ECE 127', 'http://ssahmed.buet.ac.bd', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-12-17 06:07:27', '2020-02-23 04:54:35'),
(2, 'Dr. Satya Prasad Majumder', 'dr-satya-prasad-majumder', 2, 'spmajumder@eee.buet.ac.bd', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">PhD, IIT Kharagpur, 1991</span><u1:p></u1:p><u2:p></u2:p><o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">MSc, BUET, 1985</span><u3:p></u3:p></span><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</span><u2:p></u2:p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">BSC, BUET, 1981</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '+88 01819 198 050', '20191218_1576645140.jpg', 2, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n1.	F. H. Tithi and S. P. Majumder, “Performance analysis of a DCO-CO-OFDM optical transmission system with distributed Raman amplifier using coherent heterodyne receiver,” Optik, vol. 210, 164481, May 2020.\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n2.	B. Barua and S. P. Majumder, “Performance analysis of a STBC FDM FSO communication system with direct detection receiver under turbulent condition,” Journal of Optical Communications, pp. 1-7, 2019.', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">\r\nOpto-electronics & Photonics, Optical Fiber Communication Systems, DWDM Optical Networks, Soliton Propagation, Broadband Wireless Communications, Mobile and Infra-red Networks. \r\n\r\n', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">\r\nSatya Prasad Majumder is Professor, Department of Electrical and Electronic Engineering (EEE), Bangladesh University of Engineering & Technology (BUET). Since joining BUET in 1981, he served in various positions in the department, faculty and university levels, including Head of the EEE department at BUET from June 2006 – May 2008. He was the Dean of the Faculty of EEE, BUET during June 2010 to June 2012. He served as Visiting Professor in the Faculty of Engineering (FoE) of Multimedia University (MMU), Cyberjaya, Selangor, Malaysia during Jan 1999 to July 2002. He was a Visiting Research Professor in the department of Electrical Engineering of Gunma University (Japan) during Dec 2001 to Jan 2002. He was a visiting researcher in the department of Information Engineering of University of Parma (Italy) during 1996 and 997. He worked as a consultant to the South Asian Association for Regional Co-operations (SAARC) & Dhaka Chamber of Commerce (DCC).\r\n\r\n</p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n<b>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">\r\nOn 25 June 2020, Prof. Majumder has been appointed as the Vice Chancellor of BUET.</b>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px;\">\r\nProf. Majumder supervised more than 50 MSc Theses and 6 PhD Dissertations and published more than 200 research papers in Internationally reputed refereed Journals and Conference Proceedings.\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'ECE 321', 'http://spmajumder.buet.ac.bd', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-12-17 22:59:00', '2020-02-23 04:20:29'),
