(21, 'Dr. Abdul Hasib Chowdhury', 'dr-abdul-hasib-chowdhury', 2, 'hasib@eee.buet.ac.bd', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PhD,\r\nBangladesh University of Engineering and Technology (BUET), Bangladesh, 2008</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MSc,\r\nBangladesh University of Engineering and Technology (BUET), 1995</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">BSc,&nbsp;Bangladesh\r\nUniversity of Engineering and Technology (BUET), 1992</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '+88 01711 901 568', '20191219_1576729185.jpg', 22, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1. Md Mijanur Rahman, A Hasib\r\nChowdhury, Md Alamgir Hossain, “Improved Load Frequency Control Using a Fast\r\nActing Active Disturbance Rejection Controller,” Energies, Vol 10, No. 11, Oct.\r\n2017.</span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n2. Md. Quamrul Ahsan, Abdul Hasib Chowdhury, S. Shahnawaz Ahmed, Imamul Hassan\r\nBhuyan, Mohammad Ariful Haque, and Hamidur Rahman, “Technique to Develop Auto\r\nLoad Shedding and Islanding Scheme to Prevent Power System Blackout,” IEEE\r\nTransactions on Power Systems, Vol. 27, No. 1, Feb. 2012.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Power\r\nsystem -planning and reliability, -optimization, -stability and security,\r\n-transients, -vulnerability analysis; reactive power analysis; grid code, and acts,\r\nrules, regulations, and policies related to power system; grid interconnection;\r\nblackout prevention; GICs.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Abdul Hasib Chowdhury received his\r\nB.Sc., M.Sc. and P.hD. degrees in EEE from BUET. He has been teaching at BUET\r\nsince October 1992. He has extensive teaching, research and consultancy\r\nexperience in power system -planning and reliability, -optimization, -stability\r\nand security, -transients, -vulnerability analysis; reactive power analysis;\r\ngrid code, and acts, rules, regulations, and policies related to power system;\r\ngrid interconnection; development of under-frequency load shedding and\r\nislanding schemes; GICs; renewable energy integration; power quality analysis;\r\npower plants; imparting training for the power sector in Bangladesh.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'ECE 227', 'http://hasib.buet.ac.bd', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-12-18 22:19:45', '2020-02-23 05:21:48'),
