ies of Nanostructures,\r\nand Monte Carlo Simulation. He leads the nanoscale science and technology\r\nresearch group.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>', NULL, 'http://kawsaralam.buet.ac.bd', 'https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=Eh2xHpoAAAAJ&hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-12-18 22:48:27', '2020-12-11 11:49:17'),
